OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FBy ITV News Multimedia Producer Connor
OL,8,FParker
OL,10,FDynamic pricing is already prevalent
OL,11,Fin the travel and music industries,
OL,12,Fbut could it be coming for your weekly
OL,13,Fshop?
OL,15,FThe Bank of England has recently said
OL,16,Fthe introduction of digital price
OL,17,Flabels instead of physical paper
OL,18,Flabels could open the door for
OL,19,Fsupermarkets to rapidly adjust prices
OL,20,Fon their goods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FSupermarkets have fiercely pushed back
OL,8,Fagainst the idea, saying the labels
OL,9,Fwill help reduce workload and paper
OL,10,Fwaste and won't be used for dynamic
OL,11,Fpricing.
OL,13,FBut consumer expert Martyn James told
OL,14,FITV News there would be very little
OL,15,Fpolicing of any policy and pointed out
OL,16,F"when companies aren't under scrutiny,
OL,17,Fsometimes the temptation can get a
OL,18,Flittle bit too much."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
