OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FDynamic pricing is the concept of
OL,8,Fcharging more for something when
OL,9,Fdemand is high and lowering it when
OL,10,Fdemand is low.
OL,12,FIt is a well-established tactic, just
OL,13,Fask anyone with children how expensive
OL,14,Fbooking a holiday over the summer
OL,15,Fbreak is compared to term time.
OL,17,FSupermarkets themselves already engage
OL,18,Fin it in some way, after all, Easter
OL,19,FEggs are cheapest the day after Easter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FBut recent innovations, especially
OL,8,Fwith artificial intelligence has
OL,9,Fallowed many industries to consider
OL,10,Fimplementing it in a more rapid and
OL,11,Ftargeted way.
OL,13,FIn a recent blog post, the Bank of
OL,14,FEngland said: "Technology has also
OL,15,Fallowed businesses to collect, process
OL,16,Fand store more data on consumers and
OL,17,Ftheir shopping preferences.
OL,19,F"Meanwhile, machine learning models
OL,20,Fare enabling more finely tuned price
OL,21,Fsetting using this data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,F"Instead of relying on simple rules
OL,8,Flike peak and off-peak fares, firms
OL,9,Fincreasingly deploy predictive models
OL,10,Fthat infer demand curves and monitor
OL,11,Fcompetitors to optimise their own
OL,12,Fprices."
OL,14,FThe Bank also pointed to the growth of
OL,15,Felectronic shelf labels as a
OL,16,F"technology that could enable dynamic
OL,17,Fpricing in the future."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FThe Co-op has already begun using
OL,8,Felectronic shelf labels in its stores
OL,9,Fin recent years, and several other big
OL,10,Fchains have suggested they may bring
OL,11,Fthem in.
OL,13,FWhen the Co-op introduced the labels,
OL,14,Fthey said they would "improve the
OL,15,Fcustomer shopping experience, enhance
OL,16,Fthe transparency of product
OL,17,Finformation, improve inventory
OL,18,Fmanagement and cut paper waste
OL,19,Fassociated with traditional shelf
OL,20,Flabels" as well as reduce the workload
OL,21,Ffor their staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FBut the recent BoE article has led to
OL,8,Ffears that supermarkets could rapidly
OL,9,Fchange their prices to reflect
OL,10,Fdifferent situations.
OL,12,FFor example, what if it rained and all
OL,13,Fof a sudden your local shop changed
OL,14,Fits electronic label to make an
OL,15,Fumbrella more expensive?
OL,17,FBut this idea has been flatly rejected
OL,18,Fby the British Retail Consortium (BRC).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FSpeaking on behalf of several major
OL,8,Fsupermarkets, Andrew Opie, Director of
OL,9,FFood & Sustainability at the BRC, told
OL,10,FITV News: "Supermarkets do not use,
OL,11,Fand have no plan to use, dynamic or
OL,12,Fsurge pricing in their stores. Digital
OL,13,Fpricing displays allow retailers to
OL,14,Fupdate and check thousands of prices
OL,15,Fin an effective way, so they can
OL,16,Fcontinue to offer great value for
OL,17,Fcustomers."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FSupermarkets would likely face intense
OL,8,Fbacklash if they introduced such a
OL,9,Fscheme, and with such intense
OL,10,Fcompetition between big stores, any
OL,11,Fintroduction of dynamic pricing could
OL,12,Frisk customers changing their shopping
OL,13,Fhabits.
OL,15,FBut when speaking to ITV News, James
OL,16,Fpointed out that while supermarkets
OL,17,Falready use a form of dynamic pricing
OL,18,Fto an extent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FJames pointed out: "The wonderful
OL,8,Fworld of pricing in supermarkets is
OL,9,Falready complicated and confused by
OL,10,Fspecial offers and buy one, get one
OL,11,Ffree and limited time deals and
OL,12,Fseasonal deals and different prices in
OL,13,Fdifferent parts of the country and
OL,14,Fdepending on the size of the
OL,15,Fsupermarket."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FJames argued ultimately "goods are
OL,8,Fonly ever worth what you're willing to
OL,9,Fpay for them anyway," and with fears
OL,10,Fof significant food inflation already
OL,11,Fon the horizon due to the Iran war,
OL,12,Fthe problem might not be dynamic
OL,13,Fpricing.
OL,15,FThe Food and Drink Federation (FDF)
OL,16,Fwarned last week that food inflation
OL,17,Fcould soar by more than 9% by the end
OL,18,Fof the year, up from the 3.2% that it
OL,19,Fhad forecast in September last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775782987
OL,3,CIs dynamic pricing coming to UK
OL,4,Csupermarkets and could it affect your
OL,5,Cfood shop?
OL,7,FThe shift has been caused by the
OL,8,Feffective closure of the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz and disruption and damage to
OL,10,Fenergy infrastructure in the Middle
OL,11,FEast, and even with the recent
OL,12,Fceasefire, some rises are still
OL,13,Finevitable.
OL,15,FThis means the average UK shopper is
OL,16,Ffacing a reality where their weekly
OL,17,Ffood shop goes up permanently rather
OL,18,Fthan flexibly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
